[DQR.IFRS.0138.9839] The filing does not report the element StatementOfFinancialPositionAbstract in any presentation linkroles. According to ESMA filing rules this abstract item must be reported as the root element of a Statement of Financial Position appearing in the filing.
Rule Element Id:9839 Rule version: 18.0.0RC1 -

[DQR.IFRS.0138.9840] The filing does not report either the element IncomeStatementAbstract or StatementOfComprehensiveIncomeAbstract in any presentation linkroles. According to ESMA filing rules this abstract item must be reported as the root element of a Income Statement or StatementOfComprehensiveIncomeAbstract appearing in the filing.
Rule Element Id:9840 Rule version: 18.0.0RC1 -

[DQR.IFRS.0138.9841] The filing does not report the element StatementOfCashFlowsAbstract in any presentation linkroles. According to ESMA filing rules this abstract item must be reported as the root element of a Statement Of Cash Flows appearing in the filing.
Rule Element Id:9841 Rule version: 18.0.0RC1 -
